<p>[3] T. Brown et al., "Language Models are Few-Shot Learners," Advances in Neural Information Processing Systems, vol. 33, pp. 1877-1901, 2020.</p>
<p>[4] J. Devlin et al., "BERT: Pre-training of Deep Bidirectional Transformers for Language Understanding," in Proc. NAACL-HLT, 2019.</p>
